    public class BladeRunner

    Created by ViRGiL7 on 10.02.2017. Project: library-test

    The use of replicants on Earth is banned and they are exclusively utilized for dangerous or menial work on off-world colonies.

    Replicants who defy the ban and return to Earth are hunted down and killed ("retired") by special police operatives known as "Blade Runners".

    To make job done Blade Runner should:

    - find suspect

    - make turing test for suspect

    - profit
